nodes.text: The forensic science commander was the rank given to V2A DAZ of the Galactic Republic's Coruscant Security Force during the Clone Wars. The forensic science commander provided forensic science reports in support of homicide investigations. After the murder of Senator Onaconda Farr, Inspector Lieutenant Tanivos Exantor Divo received a forensic report from the forensic science commander detailing that poison was found in Farr's body.
